#DAY 18 of our 30DaysofML series  

Today's Topic : Naive Bayes 

1. Simplilearn offers a clear explanation of Naive Bayes with the underlying Bayes' Theorem:  https://www.analyticsvidhya.com/blog/2017/09/naive-bayes-explained/ 

2. If you're comfortable with probability, GeeksforGeeks gives a more mathematical treatment:  https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/naive-bayes-classifiers/

Additional Resource : https://www.datacamp.com/tutorial/naive-bayes-scikit-learn 

